  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Pulpit Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verse 4.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "I looked on my right hand, and beheld, but there was no man that would know me",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". I looked about, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "i",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "e",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "., for human aid, but there was no one who would so much as know me. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "I was utterly deserted in my trouble. Refuge failed me.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " I had nowhere to flee unto - no safe and sure abiding-place. The \"cave of Adullam\" was but a miserable spot to hide in. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "No man cared for my soul",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; or, \"looked after my soul\" (comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Jeremiah 30:17",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Psalm 142:4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
